            "title": "RWC: Sales and profit declined year-over-year, with a US4.0 cents per share interim distribution declared",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Net sales declined 4.6% year-over-year to $645.4 million, with EBITDA down 22.2% and net profit after tax down 34.9%. Directors declared a US4.0 cents per share interim distribution, split between a cash dividend and share buy-back, amid ongoing cost-saving efforts and challenging market conditions.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Areport%3Aquartr.com%3A2850516-e8b748ff6040ecff32abaf90e5ad71fe\" target=\"_blank\">Reliance Worldwide Corp. Ltd. [RWC] Interim report — Feb. 16 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-aHOVUrmQ disclaimer-fTXt4Wkx\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-aHOVUrmQ\"><span class=\"heading-aHOVUrmQ\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-aHOVUrmQ link-with-underline-aHOVUrmQ\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
